144
00:09:24,963 --> 00:09:26,131
Mulai besok.

145
00:09:26,840 --> 00:09:28,466
Kenapa tak dibiarkan saja?

146
00:09:28,550 --> 00:09:30,969
Memangnya kau mau menikah?
Kenapa mendadak?

147
00:09:31,052 --> 00:09:33,221
Kau bisa mandi di kamar mandi itu?

148
00:09:33,304 --> 00:09:35,432
Aku hanya merenovasi kamar mandi tua.

149
00:09:35,515 --> 00:09:37,225
Mereka sementara tinggal di rumahku.

150
00:09:38,059 --> 00:09:39,394
Bagaimana dengan U-ju imutku?

151
00:09:39,477 --> 00:09:42,022
Dia ke Changwon bersama Bibi Wang.

152
00:09:42,105 --> 00:09:44,858
Seok-hyeong,
bukankah kau minum terlalu banyak?

153
00:09:44,941 --> 00:09:47,193
Berhenti minum kola.
Ini sudah kaleng ketiga.

154
00:09:47,277 --> 00:09:49,612
Lebih baik minum bir saja.
Tidak akan ada panggilan.

155
00:09:49,696 --> 00:09:50,613
Dasar naif!

156
00:09:50,947 --> 00:09:53,742
Wahai, Bubuk Kacang.
Kau seperti keluargaku.

157
00:09:55,493 --> 00:09:57,454
Bubuk ini hancur bagai keluargaku, ya?

158
00:09:57,537 --> 00:09:58,538
Benar juga.

159
00:09:59,247 --> 00:10:01,249
Sama seperti keluargamu. Ya, ‘kan?

160
00:10:01,791 --> 00:10:04,627
Keluargamu memang hancur. Astaga.

161
00:10:04,919 --> 00:10:06,504
Ayahmu sungguh...

162
00:10:08,673 --> 00:10:10,884
Ada apa dengan ayahmu?

163
00:10:11,217 --> 00:10:12,886
Dia selingkuh,

164
00:10:12,969 --> 00:10:15,972
dan menghasut karyawan
untuk transaksi organ.

165
00:10:16,056 --> 00:10:18,099
Tahun lalu
dituntut karena pelalaian pajak,

166
00:10:18,183 --> 00:10:20,101
bayar biaya restitusi sepuluh miliar won.

167
00:10:22,437 --> 00:10:24,272
Hei, kau tidak ada sesuatu?

168
00:10:24,564 --> 00:10:26,107
- Aku?
- Bilang saja.

169
00:10:30,195 --> 00:10:31,613
Saat kuliah tingkat satu,

170
00:10:32,655 --> 00:10:34,657
aku ke basemen untuk berlatih band.

171
00:10:34,741 --> 00:10:38,328
Aku datang paling pertama.
lalu berlatih drum sendiri,

172
00:10:38,620 --> 00:10:40,246
dan ayah Seok-hyeong turun.

173
00:10:41,498 --> 00:10:43,625
Dia memintaku belikan sebungkus rokok.

174
00:10:45,502 --> 00:10:46,920
- Lalu?
- Jangan bilang...

175
00:10:49,297 --> 00:10:50,840
Dia tidak memberi uangnya.

176
00:10:52,884 --> 00:10:54,052
Dia masih belum bayar.

177
00:10:54,135 --> 00:10:56,721
